<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Lastnight I was hunting Middle Split Paw spire with a few friends. Spawns were slow so I hit tracking to see if anything good was about and Lo and behold Quillmane was there. She was due east of the middle spire and heading straight toward us. I plinked her and at lvl 29 she conned yellow to me. I must say a magnificent creature though.<BR>
We slew her and I aquired the cloak. And yes it is a Mantle which is rather dissapointing as I like my BS mantle and would gladly ditch my Cloak of the Ice bear in favor of this beauty if it were to change to Back slot.</font></td></tr></table>
