<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am unsure if Pegasus has a specific spawn time or weather he/she is a random spawn. I have killed her twice and gotten 2 cloaks. Im lvl 29 and it conned yellow but was an easy kill due to me being able to kite. I did see it kill a lvl 39 ranger. Be aware that it can out run sow so be quick w/the snare. The 2nd cloak it dropped i did an /ooc that i got one and recieved a tell and soon found myself 5000pp richer and a few items worth nearly 1000pp. My best guess for getting it to spawn would be to kill all the little stuff in the zone. I'm willing to bet its just a random spawn. Good luck<BR>
<BR>
Alanna<BR>
Bristlebane</font></td></tr></table>
