<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>After reading these posts I've come to the conclusion that I must have the worst luck in EQ.  <g><BR>
<BR>
I've killed Quillmane four times and got the legs each time.  ppffbb.. I keep hoping that one day my luck will change with this great winged horse.<BR>
<BR>
I'd like to see more info about her spawn times if anyone has additional information.  Since there are several rares in SK I'm more apt to believe that her spawn isn't time based but event based.  She may be in the random encounter table as well.  Maybe I can get more info out of the Verant guys at CGDC this year. <g><BR>
<BR>
Oh, btw, I followed her trail from the north tower at the Aviak City, through the left side (facing north) of PAW, then she heads due north and flys across the skeletons by the stone bridge (heading to the centaur camp).<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
