<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is a great item to get, and yes, she does make it to Splitpaw.  That is where my group killed her.  And I find that you CAN keep casting levitate on yourself, as with any spell, so long as you are standing still.  The way I read one of the earlier posts, it sounded like you would have to wait for the spell to wear off, but you don't.</font></td></tr></table>
