<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I must say after reading everything here, I am probably the luckiest person around! I was messing around with the gnolls today when this great big white horsey came flying by...My friend and I, quickly decided it was much nicer than the gnolls, so I led the 3 we were fighting away while my druid friend killed it...And tada! we have the cloak! She let me have it too since she can cast lev anytime. I've hunted in SK for about a month real time and have only seen it this once! So all of you with plans of camping should beware! Also be careful...people have no problem with trying to kill steal it, even though you've shouted that you are fighting it...<BR>
<BR>
Now I can fly and am very happy!! Good luck all horsey slayers!</font></td></tr></table>
